@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_srtmtr(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v2 = wp.exp(v0)
    v0 = (v1 + 0.49)
    v2 = ((v2 * wp.abs(tmp + 0.94)) / (wp.sin(v0 + 0.89) * wp.exp(tmp + 0.69)))
    v1 = wp.exp(wp.abs((v0 + 0.51 * v1 + 0.63)))
    tmp = wp.sin(0.97)
    data[tid] = v0
